tor，你整唔到隻藥專係打佢。<br />\n病毒肺炎就係，隻病毒潛左入你d cells度，可能somehow你免疫系統知道果粒cell己經變左鬼，走去打佢，所以發炎。又或者隻毒潛左入粒cell度，改左粒cell的基因，觸發佢自殺。你身體為左清廢物，所以又發炎。<br />\n但我個疑問就係，佢改變基因。重可以潛伏ge.....咁其實會唔會進化到一個點，佢改到你生cancer都得?好似肝炎病毒，或HPV咁?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:23:00.000Z","msg":"絕對可以好似hepatitis B 咁搞到生肝癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2449201e3efa6829677bb6106b617d8bb08a93a","tid":1918713,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe90d0a9e2c09dcb8a0f309132aebed42ef6243","tid":1918713,"uid":177578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf227283836752f31aa4bde01dd32f6f555ad532","tid":1918713,"uid":49853,"like":105,"dislike":3,"score":102,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:32:09.000Z","msg":"好似疱疹咁<br />\n中一次就成世跟住你<br />\n久唔久又復發"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"仲話有抗要全球人7成有抗體<br />\n信佢一成<br />\n雙目失明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:23:56.000Z","msg":"佢意思係死足晒無抗體既人就完 但唔可以咁講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc001f6e6497bd1844f6f090deea8e7c20615ba3","tid":1918713,"uid":34551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"呢度野仲邊信得過日本醫療<br />\n話唔定日本個邊都係9測出陰性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42b95b4b3287e7c7a76ac2ce803f98550e92fa6","tid":1918713,"uid":3297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"根本隻毒好撚勁，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快D復工復課啦"},{"pid":"c262816eeacba4d83ccc3d444b0e0999eff827c4","tid":1918713,"uid