造成咩破壞。<br />\n講真，喂，你話有肺炎姐，咁佢係咪淨係得一個effect?呢個effect你見到咁解之嘛。<br />\n大佬，例如HPV都N咁多種，有d生椰菜花，有d生cancer. 但都有機會dormance 廿年。你依家呢隻乜鬼病毒又係咁變種。我想問，點知佢真正effect係咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"係冇人知<br />\n只可以執行當下最好既應變措施"},{"pid":"bf99d5cb5093fbfc88318c3d4ab85a938369b0c7","tid":1918713,"uid":283222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d9232248d746f3d5135c7698472c5f14d97d157","tid":1918713,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T10:59:42.000Z","msg":"係日本人驗得廢定隻菌勁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:44:26.000Z","msg":"係唔想條數太多，經濟影響好大嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b353451dfa258a645e7ea8a863ef37eccec3716d","tid":1918713,"uid":36690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:45:28.000Z","msg":"3萬，復發，thanks"},{"pid":"80b7d53f9333370e24fb7451a92c0e4925777d68","tid":1918713,"uid":198932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44a56d31e4ac913363eed78b5dc80a138f155dd0","tid":1918713,"uid":25952,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"9557079bed13d1631623dd261ebc54ce5f01aeaf","tid":1918713,"uid":171849,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"<code>本身有長期病患、免疫力低下、腎臟功能問題等</code><br />\n<br />\n咁佢中左都好大獲下"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"正常佢呢種情況 應該9死1生先係<br />\n有無可能係日本驗錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T11:47:32.000Z","msg":"其實所有測試都唔係100%準<br />\n有好多因素影響:例如抽鼻水去驗, sample唔新鮮, or條友剛剛先中左招病毒含量太低都會detect唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以一定先要recheck幾次"},{"pid":"95ec745ecdcf5b958270f66a29b8bcb6ceed2cac","tid":1918713,"uid":87471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":